Tuwapun（華東部落）

Itiniay i Hualien Cen no Hualien ko Tuwapun a niyaro’, 1,682  ko sa’osi no parod no loma’, 4,170 ko sa’osi no tamdaw.

20% ko ka’aloman no Yincomin, polong han i, 816  ko tamdaw; o roma sato i, 80% ko ka’aloman no roma a finacadan, polong han i, 3,354 ko tamdaw.

O pa-sin-to(百分比) no ka’aloman no tamdaw no kasafinacadan i, ko Amis13%, Truku2%, Bunun2%, Tayal1%, Paiwan1%, roma1%.

Ira ko picodadan(美崙國中) i niyaro’.

